{"tid":1190706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會法律顧問再就修訂逃犯條例致函保安局要求澄清","createTime":"2019-06-07T13:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T13:35:00.000Z","uid":1441,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51d91f343d46daffda46f60d11193b872f52eddc","tid":1190706,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"立法會高級助理法律顧問曹志遠再度致函保安局，要求就逃犯條例修訂多點作澄清，包括法官是否可考慮在《逃犯條例》無明確交代的其他因素及人權保障。<br />\n<br />\n曹志遠在信中要求當局澄清，檢查個案是否「錯誤、不公或壓迫」，是由法官按《逃犯條例》在交付審判程序中使用，抑或只能由行政長官運用。而在相關程序中，法官能否考慮在逃犯條例，以及修例後特別個案移交協議以外的其他因素或有關人權的保障。而縱使移交個案滿足到《逃犯條例》的要求，法官是否有剩餘酌情權決定，不作移交。<br />\n<br />\n立法會法律顧問在信中引用以往案例，指出行政長官下達移交逃犯的命令，並不慣常解釋行政決定原因，立法機構亦無要求特首交代原因，而在普通法中，亦無相關義務，因此要求保安局澄清，行政長官按法例是否要解釋移交逃犯的決定。<br />\n<br />\n法律顧問又要求當局澄清，行政長官以及法庭在考慮移交問題時，會否考慮起訴罪行的時效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461462-20190607.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461462-20190607.htm&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ukv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=47444177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461462-20190607.htm&h=8c2ff250\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461462-20190607.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0749ce5e6b4bef38b209c3fcbb90f857a6228448","tid":1190706,"uid":16365,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上呀曹志遠<br />\n唔好撚放過保安局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a17a65eea09c87468d364a54754ca0c913b406f","tid":1190706,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"真係寧願劉華做保安局局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe428c0cdeef694e963d2509b2c435efb788b65","tid":1190706,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd61d807a54ce8e8f2c37a074aa3aa2ffa563f6b","tid":1190706,"uid":155374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"錄音：逃犯條例中沒寫入額外保障是為了保持靈活性，又指申請移交的一方必須要遵循協議，落實當中的人權保障。<br />\n<br />\n保持靈活性以便選擇性落實有關保障。"},{"pid":"5851f1c35b41ebb9cd0691e2eb22554f9b8afe6e","tid":1190706,"uid":14478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"早兩日法庭先判左唔洗理受唔受人道對待"},{"pid":"34dacd033073edc804cc17001accc71b8937a062","tid":1190706,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"相信個顧問覺得到時特首會以錄音機式話個別事件唔評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}